Output assets/quick_start_2.gif
Require dart
Set Margin 0
Set BorderRadius 0
Set WindowBar ""
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 950
Set Height 400
Set Padding 10
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "clear && dart run example/quick_start_2.dart"
Enter
Show

Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Up
Sleep 500ms
Type "ru"
Sleep 500ms
Sleep 1s
